title: Meteora 2012 DVDRip Sonata Premiere
description:
A monk and a nun, from two neighboring monasteries in Meteora, fall in love and are forced to choose between God and themselves. It all sounds very schematic, but in the hands of Spiros Stathoulopoulos this familiar, potentially melodramatic, story is transformed into something as spare and beautiful as a byzantine psalm.


Languages: Greek / Russian

Subs srt: Portuguese / English
